00:17:29.390 --> 00:17:30.950
But where we're spending a lot of our time

00:17:30.950 --> 00:17:32.240
and where we're very interested is

00:17:32.240 --> 00:17:33.710
what is the front end of AI?

00:17:33.710 --> 00:17:35.300
How are people actually going to interact

